/*STD *  RPGBASE                                                      *
/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas BoE Composite Currencies Report')                *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Bank of England                                      *
      *                                                               *
      *  BY3060 - Composite Currencies Report                         *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This program prints a report of Composite         *
      *             Currencies                                        *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: mmCnnnn - (program name)                          *
      *                                                               *
      *  (c) Finastra International Limited 1997                      *
      *                                                               *
